metadata.name: RunGo Dash for Dogs 2022 Finishers Medal
metadata.description: These digital race achievement medals honour real-world accomplishments by commemorating them on the blockchain. RunGo Dash for Dogs 2022 is the 8th annual fundraiser event, a guided 10km, 5km, or 2km run or walk through Stanley Park in Vancouver, BC, with proceeds going to BC and Alberta Guide Dogs. This fun and non-competitive race takes you through the beautiful trails in Stanley Park.
